4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"9e88e9939119dfefbcf135089b8e407d93bd0d03","tid":642302,"uid":157453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T17:16:54.000Z","msg":"典解台積電可以勁咁多？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T17:19:36.000Z","msg":"台積電的創立，起始於1986年由臺灣的工業技術研究院（工研院）與荷蘭的飛利浦電子公司簽約合資成立半導體製造公司，由當時工研院院長張忠謀帶著一群以出身工研院為主的工程師一同籌辦，而工研院的半導體技術則主要來自1970年代中期，<span style=\"color: red;\">由經濟部出資1000萬美元的RCA技術移轉計劃。</span>台積電成立後，張忠謀遂出任董事長迄今。台積電於1994年在臺灣證券交易所掛牌上市，1997年台積電到美國發行美國存託憑證（ADR），並在美國紐約證券交易所（NYSE）以TSM為代號開始掛牌交易。<br />\n<br />\n買人地科技<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b009aae4a78226c9e05a9016da4b556d7f2bb38","tid":642302,"uid":59487,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T17:20:53.000Z","msg":"贏國近年發展得最快既唔係 玻璃芯 咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a40f629fb99787e5a172572e2816db436445014","tid":642302,"uid":127988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T17:21:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/26/012109_95d9845b1b8041e6454488cbd84e6c67.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F26%2F012109_95d9845b1b8041e6454488cbd84e6c67.jpg&h=162fffd5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"062fae291d79c97899eb54c5f3b495a477abf7b3","tid":642302,"uid":127988,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"3a40f629fb99787e5a172572e2816db436445014","tid":642302,"uid":127988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T17:21:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/26/012109_95d9845b1b8041e6454488cbd84e6c67.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F26%2F012109_95d9845b1b8041e6454488cbd84e6c67.jpg&h=162fffd5&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T17:22:43.000Z","msg":"蔣經國內閣開始一連串的經濟發展計畫。1973年，擔任經濟部長的孫運璿建議倣傚韓國的「科技研究院」，成立以政府資金為主的半官方機構工業技術研究院，以財團法人的方式突破政府法規限制，以高薪聘請歸國學人，從事產業研發。當時立法院認為工研院乃政府出資，卻因財團法人之地位，政府並沒有管理權而大力反對，立委稱此為「化公為私」，認為此例一開，將後患無窮。孫運璿因此多方奔走，與立法院溝通，最後該案僅以勉強超過50%的同意，獲得通過。孫運璿也因此被稱為「工研院之父」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">CMOS是當時RCA計畫中選定的轉移技術，也是日後積體電路的主流技術<br />\n1974年2月，孫運璿與行政院秘書長費驊和時任美國無線電公司（RCA）研究室主任的潘文淵在台北市林森北路小欣欣豆漿店討論一小時後，決定將半導體產業為台灣1970年代中期之後的經濟發展重點，並成立工研院技術顧問委員會，自RCA技術移轉，取得了積體電路的技術。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50d989d4007c8c05b3bd4b98565f883b53d8a40e","tid":642302,"uid":95404,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T17:31:30.000Z","msg":"芯佢老母片咩 香港就叫開晶片嘅"},{"pid":"fa9fdc7250ca65b1b3f04752d9a01c2856a6a0b3","tid":642302,"uid":128261,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T17:32:51.000Z","msg":"支那又～～～～～～贏！"},{"pid":"b3f5b5876835bcd2513ada3c7e629a3227aa0a61","tid":642302,"uid":165782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"006ec486b96e7c3de6b51d74250cd3445ad5f54e","tid":642302,"uid":14918,"like":38,"dislike":1,"score":37,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T16:38:11.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: navy;\">中興事件未夠一個月<br />\n<br />\n個差距就縮得咁快</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T17:58:10.000Z","msg":"贏"},{"pid":"82a72d7687852c877c473816b12ab7016b66dfb8","tid":642302,"uid":170159,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-25T17:59:33.000Z","msg":"幾時有龍芯438？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7277f9635ff91